review_blob: Winter Beard was a slight disappointment. I think I was searching for the deep chocolate or cranberry tastes, but only barely came through at the ends. An excellent stout with extremely solid balance of sweetness and bitterness, but lacking the solid as-advertised chocolate cranberry flavors apart from the barest of hints on the back end.
beer_name: Muskoka Winter Beard Double Chocolate Cranberry Stout
